{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">了解钠的物理性质，知道钠在空气中会被氧化。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">钠的密度比水小，常保存在煤油或石蜡油中。质软，可用小刀切割。新切开的钠有银白色金属光泽，在空气中很快被氧化，银白色逐渐褪去。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\">4Na + O</span><sub><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\">2</span></sub><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;= 2Na</span><sub><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\">2</span></sub><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\">O</span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"用品","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">仪器：镊子、滤纸、玻璃片、小刀。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">药品：钠。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">用镊子取一块钠放在滤纸上，点击滤纸，吸干钠表面的煤油。将钠放到玻璃片上，用小刀切一小块钠。将较大的钠用镊子放回试剂瓶中，观察新切开的钠表面的颜色和光泽。一段时间后，观察钠表面有何变化。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"现象","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">新切开的钠表面有银白色金属光泽，在空气中放置一段时间后银白色逐渐褪去。</span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}